These Monster Cookie Oat Cups are our latest obsession! Our friend @Fit Foodie Finds created this viral recipe and we are hooked! With a peanut butter base, layers of more peanut butter, chocolate, and mini M&Ms, it’s the perfect sweet treat to have on hand. Plus, they chill and freeze perfectly!
Oat Layer
2 c quick-cooking oats
½ c honey
⅓ c peanut butter
⅓ c mini chocolate chips
Chocolate Layer
6 oz. dark chocolate chopped
2 tsp coconut oil
Peanut Butter Layer
½ c all-natural creamy peanut butter
1 tsp coconut oil
¼ c mini M&M’s
2 tbsp mini chocolate chips
Head to Fit Foodie Finds for the full recipe
#peanutbutter #dessert #chocolate #healthier #easyrecipes #fooddolls
